stability is implied by this permission.

This repository also depends on the APCA contrast algorithm (apca-w3.js),
copyright © 2019-2022 Andrew Somers / Myndex Research, used under the
W3 license for web content accessibility purposes.

The original tooling in this repository (the CLI, MCP server, and
sandbox web app — see NOTICE for the file breakdown) is not yet released
under a declared open-source license.

